longBusinessSummary: Sanwaria Consumer Limited is under corporate insolvency resolution process. Previously, it was engaged in production and sale of basmati rice and refined oil in India. The company was formerly known as Sanwaria Agro Oils Limited and changed its name to Sanwaria Consumer Limited in August 2017. Sanwaria Consumer Limited was incorporated in 1991 and is based in Bhopal, India.
